name: NeoCubes
description:
The basic principles of magnetism and mathematics allow you to build geometric and complex patterns.

Neocubes have 6 faces, 12 edges, and 8 vertices made from 216 neodymium magnetic spheres. The magnetic field strength of one neodymium sphere is 6000x greater than Earth's magnetic field.

- Crypto Resonance
